metadata.name: Swag Skull #1
metadata.description: The Swag Skulls Collection is Swag Golf's genesis NFT collection. The collection consists of 3333 unique Skulls that could be used for early and guaranteed access to products, as well as entry to events and other exclusive Swag experiences. Skulls are our most popular headcover design, and we've done hundreds of versions of them for years now...just with sewing machines.
